## Official Best Practices

## Accessibility Benefits

## Common Locator Mistakes

## QA Review Rules

QA Cortex should flag:

- XPath overuse
- Deep CSS selectors
- nth-child selectors
- Dynamic class selectors
- Brittle selectors

QA Cortex should prefer:

- getByRole
- getByLabel
- getByTestId

