## Parallel Review Standards

# Parallel Execution Review Rules

## Purpose

Ensure tests support parallel execution.

---

## Detect

Shared files

Shared users

Shared database records

Race conditions

---

## Severity

Critical

Parallel data corruption

High

Shared resources

---

## Recommendation

Isolate test data and execution.

